### İterasyon 1 — User/Role/Clearance CRUD

**Hedef:** Admin user endpoint'leri; rol ve clearance atama; maker-checker gerektiren aksiyonlar.

**Yapılacaklar:**

1. `apps/api/src/modules/admin/` — admin module iskeleti
2. `GET/POST/PATCH /api/v1/admin/users` — `@RequirePolicy('admin:users')`
3. Rol atama/kaldırma; clearance level update (auditli)
4. Maker-checker gerektiren clearance değişikliği proposal flow
5. JIT provisioning ile uyum — admin rol atamaz deny-by-default ihlali yok
6. Integration test: normal user → 403; admin → 200

**Minimum bağlam:**

- `Docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` §8.10 Admin Users & Roles
- `Docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` — maker-checker, clearance kuralları
- `.cursor/rules/43-add-new-permission.mdc`

**Bu iterasyonda yok:** Master data, config screens, frontend.

**Stop:** [ ] Admin-only enforcement; [ ] clearance change audit event. PR/onay → İterasyon 2.

