## Constraints

### Use

- Maker-checker backend enforced — maker ≠ checker
- Admin FieldMasking — no report_text/incident_description
- CSV export async job + presigned URL
- Generic master-data `/:type` pattern
- KVKK publish destructive confirmation
- System settings bulk update atomic tx
- Template preview backend render

### Avoid

- Maker-checker frontend-only
- Audit viewer unredacted content
- Client-side CSV export large datasets
- 8 duplicate master data controllers
- Admin viewing case ethical content
- KVKK publish without confirmation

